cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with information theoretic aspects of secure communication, specifically the two-way wiretap channel. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses cryptography and security, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The experimental setup involves sensor boards, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization and control, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses experimental results, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
